      <p>
      Lynne Truss's &quot;Eats, Shoots &amp; Leaves&quot; is a delightful
      read about using punctuation correctly in English sentences.

      m4_begin_post_rest
      <div class="book_display">
        <img src="m4_root_dir/books/images/esl.jpg"
